In England, in the seven days to 14 November, there were 222,096 new confirmed cases (392.7 new cases per 100,000). In the seven days to 07 November, there were 192,228 new cases and so the new cases have risen by 16% (29,868 extra cases). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 19 November is 8,281,117 (14,643.8 cases per 100,000 population).
